<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>It would be nice if you could set a default value if a validation fails or when ALLOW_EMPTY is used and no value was submitted</p>

<pre class="literal">
$validators = array( 
    'year' = array( 
        'Digits',
        'allowEmpty' =&gt; true,
        'default' =&gt; date('Y')
    ) 
);
</pre>

    </div>
