        <div class="body">
            <p>An earlier version of my proposal for Zend_Filter_Input did have the capability of defining defaults.</p>

<p>I'd like to keep this feature request open but mark it postponed.  We have a lot of other features to work on before ZF 1.0.0.  This feature would be nice, but it's not mandatory for ZF 1.0, and it can be implemented in a future release of ZF without impacting backward-compatibility.</p>

<p>In the meantime, you should handle default values as part of your application logic.</p>

